comment: * Defines SIP session states, such as "registering", "outgoing call", and "in call".

variables.name: READY_TO_CALL
variables.comment: When session is ready to initiate a call or transaction.

variables.name: REGISTERING
variables.comment: When the registration request is sent out.

variables.name: DEREGISTERING
variables.comment: When the unregistration request is sent out.

variables.name: INCOMING_CALL
variables.comment: When an INVITE request is received.

variables.name: INCOMING_CALL_ANSWERING
variables.comment: When an OK response is sent for the INVITE request received.

variables.name: OUTGOING_CALL
variables.comment: When an INVITE request is sent.

variables.name: OUTGOING_CALL_RING_BACK
variables.comment: When a RINGING response is received for the INVITE request sent.

variables.name: OUTGOING_CALL_CANCELING
variables.comment: When a CANCEL request is sent for the INVITE request sent.

variables.name: PINGING
variables.comment: When an OPTIONS request is sent.
